1. DEFINITIONS

   "License" means this document.

   "Licensor" means the copyright holder(s) named above.

   "You" (or "Your") means an individual or legal entity exercising permissions
   granted by this License.

   "Engine" means the source code, object code, compiled binaries, associated
   documentation, editor tools, and all other files of the game engine
   distributed under this License, including but not limited to the runtime,
   renderer, asset pipeline, editor (RatEditor), scripting layer, and standard
   libraries that form part of the engine itself.

   "Engine Derivative Work" means any work based on or derived from the Engine,
   including modifications, forks, ports, adaptations, and works that
   substantially incorporate the Engine's source code.

   "Game" means an interactive software application, software project, or other
   creative work that You build using the Engine, where the Engine is used as
   an underlying platform or runtime but is not itself the primary deliverable.
   A Game does not include a fork or modification of the Engine sold or
   distributed as a game engine or development tool.

   "Commercial Purpose" means any activity intended for or resulting in
   commercial advantage or monetary compensation. As it applies to the Engine
   and Engine Derivative Works specifically, Commercial Purpose includes but is
   not limited to: selling or licensing the Engine or an Engine Derivative Work;
   offering the Engine or an Engine Derivative Work as a paid service or
   subscription; bundling the Engine or an Engine Derivative Work as a component
   of a paid product; charging for access to a hosted instance of the Engine
   or Engine Derivative Work.

   "AI Training Purpose" means using the Engine, its source code, its
   documentation, or any Engine Derivative Work as training data, fine-tuning
   data, evaluation data, reinforcement learning data, or any other input to
   a machine learning or artificial intelligence system, model, or pipeline.

   "Distribute" means to make available to any third party by any means.


