   b) SAME LICENSE: Any Engine Derivative Work you Distribute must be
      licensed under this License, verbatim. You may not impose additional
      restrictions beyond those in this License, and you may not grant
      additional permissions not present in this License.

   c) SOURCE AVAILABILITY: If you Distribute a compiled or binary form of
      the Engine or an Engine Derivative Work, you must make the complete
      corresponding source code available under this License, either bundled
      with the distribution or via a publicly accessible URL that remains
      accessible for no less than three (3) years from the date of
      distribution.

   d) NON-COMMERCIAL ONLY: The Engine and any Engine Derivative Work may only
      be Distributed at no cost and for no monetary compensation. You may not
      sell, charge for, or monetize the Engine or any Engine Derivative Work
      in any form. Distribution must be free of charge.


4. COPYLEFT REQUIREMENT

   Any Engine Derivative Work must be licensed under this License in its
