5. RESTRICTIONS

   The following are expressly prohibited:

   a) COMMERCIAL USE OF THE ENGINE PROHIBITED: You may not use, Distribute,
      sell, license, or offer the Engine or any Engine Derivative Work for
      any Commercial Purpose. This prohibition covers the Engine itself and
      any fork, port, adaptation, or modification of the Engine.

      For clarity: this restriction applies to the Engine as a software
      product or tool. It does not restrict You from commercially releasing,
      selling, or distributing Games that you build using the Engine.

   b) AI TRAINING PROHIBITED: You may not use the Engine, its source code,
      its documentation, or any Engine Derivative Work for any AI Training
      Purpose, whether commercial or non-commercial.

   c) MONETIZED HOSTING: You may not offer the Engine or any Engine Derivative
      Work as a paid hosted service, software-as-a-service, or cloud platform.

   d) SUBLICENSING UNDER DIFFERENT TERMS: You may not sublicense the Engine
      or any Engine Derivative Work under any license other than this License.


6. GAMES BUILT WITH THE ENGINE

   Games that You build using the Engine are Your own creative works. This
