   Games. You may release Games under any license you choose, including
   proprietary and commercial licenses. You do not owe royalties or fees to
   the Licensor for Games you release using the Engine.

   The Engine runtime or libraries that are linked into or distributed with
   Your Game remain subject to this License. You must include a copy of this
   License and an attribution notice with any Game you distribute that bundles
   Engine binaries or source code. A brief notice in your credits, readme, or
   About screen is sufficient for attribution.


